This Rangapur has a very special feature about it. You see Shri Ramdas swami the master of .. the guru of Shivaji found the statue of  Shri Rama, Sita and Lakshmana in this river, at this point. In the Krishna river. And this was such a remarkable thing they didn't know how the statue has come there. It was taken to a place called Chafal where they put it. Now Shri Ramdas swami had created lots of Hanumanas out of the mother earth. Lot of Hanumanas out of the mother earth and [ discussion among Sahaja yogis and talking to Shri Mataji.]

Now, you see they are saying that it's better to go by buses so they are going to call one bus by one bus.

हं ठीक आहे. अं? काय? थोडे सहजयोगी घेऊन जा तू मोरेश्वर.

Some men should go.

ऐकलं का [एशीबॉईबॉ] [ unclear. Seems like Sahaja Yogi's name]. ऐकलं का तुम्ही? आधी फक्त पुरूषांना घेऊन जा. मग बायकांना हळू हळू.बायकांना नको. 

All the men can go.Few men. We’ll go last. Ah the Sahaja yogi men have to go now by buses because the police is afraid that these people might try to trouble you. So they are going to get the buses here and you all should go in the bus. Now, all the men, who are here, need not go, but quite a lot of them. There is a one bus coming. One by one you go by bus. The police one is going to look after you. Alright?